  "description": "<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 8\"><div class=\"layoutArea\"><div class=\"column\"><p><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">For your Orbital/Deep Space Settlement, Roll d50 and pick 1-2 entries from the relevant column in the Oracle. A population of “Hundreds and above” are “Medium-Large”. The results are what you first hear or smell.<br /><br />When you roll a result of “Manufacturing” on one of the Industries Oracles, roll 1d20 on the Manufacturing Oracle, referencing the relevant column for the Settlement Type.</span></p></div></div></div>",
